      "comment": "MAGICAL SAIDE (2) was fresh up last time at Maitland where she finished sixth (26.00) in a Grade 5. Will be much improved. Should be very hard to beat this time. BENTLEY RED (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (31.01) in a Grade 5/6 at Q Lakeside. Has never missed the frame at the trip from three starts. The form out of his last race has been franked. Key runner on best form. HELLO AERIAL (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a second place finish (29.87) at Gosford the start prior. One of the better chances. WHISKY BENT (6) is worth a look over a shorter distance this time.",
